<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@jblandford:matrix.org">jrb</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p>GNOME Crosswords 0.3.8 has been <a href="https://blogs.gnome.org/jrb/2023/04/02/crosswords-0-3-8-change-management/">released</a>.</p>
<p>This release adds the following improvements:</p>
<ul>
<li>&ldquo;New Puzzle&rdquo; greeter for the editor.
‚Ä¢ Fully adaptive sizing. Crosswords will shrink to fit available space
‚Ä¢ Fix end-of-game bugs where you could still edit the puzzle
‚Ä¢ Use tags instead of labels for puzzle-set metainfo
‚Ä¢ Enumeration rendering fixes
‚Ä¢ Miscelaneous bugfixes</li>
</ul>
<p>This release marks a change in focus. For the next few months, we are going to work more on the Editor than the game. Stay tuned for more changes!

